  "texts": [
    "This issue can be remedied by using data creation techniques to generate new images from the current methodology (Arbabyazd et al., 2021).",
    "The investigation in this field will continue despite the expansion of the dataset, as its efficacy remains uncertain.",
    "In addition to this, image annotation (Choi et al., 2020) is another problem.",
    "Radiologists should annotate the image data provided for certain tasks when tagging medical images.",
    "The classification process is very time-consuming."
  ]
